"  CRUST","2 3/4 cups (about 11 3/4 oz.) all-purpose flour","2 tablespoons granulated sugar","1 teaspoon kosher salt","3/4 cup cold butter, cubed","1/4 cup frozen shortening, cubed","8  to 10 Tbsp. ice water","  FILLING","1/2 cup granulated sugar","2 teaspoons ground cardamom","1 tablespoon cornstarch","6  medium peaches, ripe yet still firm","1 teaspoon fresh lemon juice","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","1 tablespoon grated fresh ginger","2 tablespoons heavy cream","1 tablespoon turbinado sugar (optional)"